proof:
Proof using WF WFSC TLSCOH IORDCOH .
    rewrite covered_in_coverable; eauto.
    rewrite issued_in_issuable at 1; eauto.
    rewrite (rmw_in_ppo_loc WF) at 1; eauto.
    apply ar_rf_ppo_loc_coverable_issuable_in_I.
    apply ar_rf_ppo_loc_coverable_issuable_in_I; auto.
    rewrite <- seq_union, dom_unionL.
    apply W_ar_coverable_issuable_in_CI.
    apply ar_rf_ppo_loc_coverable_issuable_in_I.
    apply ar_rf_ppo_loc_coverable_issuable_in_I.
    apply ar_rf_ppo_loc_coverable_issuable_in_I.
    apply ar_rf_ppo_loc_coverable_issuable_in_I.
    apply ar_rf_ppo_loc_coverable_issuable_in_I.
    apply ar_rf_ppo_loc_coverable_issuable_in_I.
    apply ar_rf_ppo_loc_coverable_issuable_in_I.
    apply ar_rf_ppo_loc_coverable_issuable_in_I.
    apply ar_rf_ppo_loc_coverable_issuable_in_I.
    apply ar_rf_ppo_loc_coverable_issuable_in_I.
    apply ar_rf_ppo_loc_coverable_in_CI.
    apply ar_rf_ppo_loc_coverable_issuable_in_I.
    apply ar_rf_ppo_loc_coverable_issuable_in_I.
    apply ar_rf_ppo_loc_coverable_issuable_in_I.
    rewrite seq_union_l, seq_union_r, dom_union; unionL.
    apply ar_rf_ppo_loc_coverable_issuable_in_I.
    apply ar_rf_ppo_loc_coverable_issuable_in_I; auto.
    rewrite (rmw_rf_ppo_loc WF) at 1; eauto with hahn.
    apply ar_rf_ppo_loc_coverable_issuable_in_I.
    apply ar_rf_ppo_loc_coverable_issuable_in_I; auto.
    apply ar_rf_ppo_loc_coverable_issuable_in_I.
    apply ar_rf_ppo_loc_coverable_issuable_in_I.
    apply ar_rf_ppo_loc_coverable_issuable_in_I.
    apply ar_rf_ppo_loc_coverable_issuable_in_I.
    apply ar_rf_ppo_loc_coverable_issuable_in_I.
    apply ar_rf_ppo_loc_coverable_in_CI.
    apply ar_rf_ppo_loc_coverable_issuable_in_I.
    apply ar_rf_ppo_loc_coverable_issuable_in_I.
    apply ar_rf_ppo_loc_coverable_issuable_in_I.
    eapply rsw_trans. { apply ar_rf_ppo_loc_coverable_issuable_in_I.
                     apply ar_rf_ppo_loc_coverable_in_CI.
                     rewrite seq_union_l, dom_union; unionL.
                     apply ar_rf_ppo_loc_coverable_issuable_in_I.
                     eapply rsw_trans. {
                     apply ar_rf_ppo_loc_coverable_issuable_in_I.
                     apply ar_rf_ppo_loc_coverable_in_CI.
                     rewrite seq_union_l, dom_union; unionL.
                     apply ar_rf_ppo_loc_coverable_issuable_in_I.
                     rewrite seq_union_l, dom_union; unionL.
                     apply ar_rf_ppo_loc_coverable_issuable_in_I.
                     rewrite seq_union_l, dom_union; unionL.
                     apply ar_rf_ppo_loc_coverable_issuable_in_I.
                     apply ar_rf_ppo_loc_coverable_issuable_in_I.
                     apply ar_rf_ppo_loc_coverable_issuable_in_I.
                     apply ar_rf_ppo_loc_coverable_issuable_in_I.
                     rewrite seq_union_l, dom_union; unionL.
                     apply ar_rf_ppo_loc_coverable_issuable_in_I.
                     apply ar_rf_ppo_loc_coverable_in_CI. }
Qed.
